(1, 'Habib Metropolitan Bank', 'From Wireframes to Amazing Results', 'habib-metropolitan-bank', 'When Habib Metropolitan Bank (HabibMetro), one of Pakistan\'s leading trade finance institutions, approached us, they were looking to refresh and modernize the brand’s digital look and feel. \nDespite having a solid base with a presence in over 200 cities and a legacy rooted in the globally recognized Habib Bank AG Zurich, their online look just wasn’t doing justice to who they are. Their website was outdated. Their mobile app lacked consistency, and the overall user experience wasn’t flowing right.\n', 'www.habibmetro.com', '[{\"image\": \"\", \"title\": \"Website Redesign\"}, {\"image\": \"\", \"title\": \"Website Redevelopment\"}, {\"image\": \"\", \"title\": \"Mobile App UX/UI\"}, {\"image\": \"\", \"title\": \"Internet Banking UX/UI\"}]', '[{\"component\": \"Content Management System\", \"technology\": \"Customized WordPress\"}, {\"component\": \"Frontend\", \"technology\": \"HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript\"}, {\"component\": \"Backend\", \"technology\": \"PHP (WordPress Core Customization)\"}, {\"component\": \"Design & Prototyping\", \"technology\": \"Figma, Adobe XD\"}, {\"component\": \"Languages Supported\", \"technology\": \"English, Urdu\"}]', NULL, '[{\"title\": \"Designing a Smooth Experience\", \"features\": [\"Clarity over clutter\", \"Consistency across web and mobile\", \"Accessibility in both English and Urdu\"], \"subtitle\": \"We brought the vision to life using a minimalist, clean, and modern design language, focusing on:\"}, {\"title\": \"The Website\", \"features\": [\"Built on a customized WordPress platform for easy updates and content management\", \"Completely responsive on all devices\", \"Optimized for bilingual support (English & Urdu)\", \"Designed to highlight HabibMetro\'s progressive banking services\"], \"subtitle\": \"\"}, {\"title\": \"The Mobile App\", \"features\": [\"Redesigned with a structured, intuitive layout\", \"Mirrored the visual consistency of the website\", \"Improved usability and flow, making tasks easier and faster for users\", \"Supported English and Urdu, ensuring inclusivity for all customer segments\"], \"subtitle\": \"\"}]', '<p className=\"fc-primary text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6\">\n                Right from the start, HabitMetro wasn\'t just after a new look — they wanted a comprehensive upgrade of their digital presence.\n              </p>\n\n              <h3 className=\"text-[22px] fc-primary font-bold mb-2\">\n                Their goals were:\n              </h3>\n\n              <p className=\"fc-primary text-lg leading-relaxed mb-1\">A website that was modern, responsive, and intuitive.</p>\n              <p className=\"fc-primary text-lg leading-relaxed mb-1\">A website that was modern, responsive, and intuitive.</p>\n              <p className=\"fc-primary text-lg leading-relaxed mb-1\">A website that was modern, responsive, and intuitive.</p>', '<p className=\"fc-primary text-lg leading-relaxed mb-2\">\n                We started by setting the groundwork. Our team created a comprehensive digital strategy, which included:\n              </p>\n\n              <p className=\"fc-primary text-lg leading-relaxed mb-1 \">A website that was modern, responsive, and intuitive.</p>\n              <p className=\"fc-primary text-lg leading-relaxed mb-1 \">A website that was modern, responsive, and intuitive.</p>\n              <p className=\"fc-primary text-lg leading-relaxed mb-1 \">A website that was modern, responsive, and intuitive.</p>', ' We took a very cooperative approach. Whether customers were using a desktop computer to examine financial products or a mobile device to check account details, every layout, interaction, and interface was designed with the end user in mind.', NULL, 'published', 0, NULL, NULL, '2025-05-26 10:32:16', '2025-05-26 10:32:16'),
(2, 'Dr. Ziauddin Hospital', 'Website Design and Development\r\n', 'dr-ziauddin-hospital', 'When Habib Metropolitan Bank (HabibMetro), one of Pakistan\'s leading trade finance institutions, approached us, they were looking to refresh and modernize the brand’s digital look and feel. \r\nDespite having a solid base with a presence in over 200 cities and a legacy rooted in the globally recognized Habib Bank AG Zurich, their online look just wasn’t doing justice to who they are. Their website was outdated. Their mobile app lacked consistency, and the overall user experience wasn’t flowing right.\r\n', 'www.ziauddinhospital.com', '[{\"image\": \"\", \"title\": \"Website UI/UX Design\"}, {\"image\": \"\", \"title\": \"Website Development\"}, {\"image\": \"\", \"title\": \"Feature Enhancement\"}, {\"image\": \"\", \"title\": \"Bug Fixes and System Optimization\"}, {\"image\": \"\", \"title\": \"Pharmacy Portal Design\"}, {\"image\": \"\", \"title\": \"Examination Board Design\"}]', NULL, 'Through collaboration with TDF, Ziauddin\'s revamped OPD/IPD Pharmacy Portal and University Examination Board Portal saw significant improvements. The portals now offer enhanced features, improved user experience with a modern design, and increased reliability through bug resolution. This successful project serves as a prime example of how transforming internal systems can lead to greater efficiency and a more robust digital foundation.\n', '[{\"title\": \"Limited Features\", \"features\": [], \"subtitle\": \"The portals lacked functionalities that could streamline administrative tasks and data management.\"}, {\"title\": \"Bugs and Issues\", \"features\": [], \"subtitle\": \"Users encountered technical glitches and bugs that hampered their workflow.\"}, {\"title\": \"Outdated Design\", \"features\": [], \"subtitle\": \"The overall design of the portals was outdated, making navigation and information retrieval cumbersome.\"}]', '<p className=\"fc-primary text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6\">\r\